Since you are informed perhaps you might also consider that over 10's of millions of years our sun's output becomes hotter (heats up because the percent of hydrogen fusion decreases as hydrogen is converted into higher molecular weight elements) during it's life (see Betelgeuse).  The sun bombards the earth with more energy now than 30,000,000 years ago.  Another factor in considering decision making based on reality rather than cherry picking or profound ignorance (see video).

